read.title: Dementia symptoms: This is the most commonly MISSED warning sign of dementia - Times of India
read.description: The most commonly missed warning sign of dementia is trouble with spatial issues, speech, and directions. Difficulty with language and visual/spatial skills can manifest before memory loss in certain cases.
